title: United Kingdom Imports - Pulp Of Wood, Fibrous Material & Waste & Scrap
description: Imports - Pulp Of Wood, Fibrous Material & Waste & Scrap in the United Kingdom decreased to 55.49 GBP Million in September from 62.77 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports - Pulp Of Wood, Fibrous Material & Waste & in the United Kingdom averaged 47.40 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 82.87 GBP Million in September of 2000 and a record low of 27.17 GBP Million in January of 2021. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Pulp of Wood, Fibrous Material & Waste.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
